Package: heidi
Title: An implementation of the HESA HEIDI API in R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Brendan", "Fawcett", role = "aut", comment = "Original author of main codebase, see http://coursedata.le.ac.uk/2013/04/29/r-and-heidi-api/"),
            person("Graham", "Parsons", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = "Package maintainer", email = "graham@grahamrp.com")
          )
Description: An implementation of the HESA HEIDI API in R. It enables
    a user to connect to the Higher Education Statistics Agency API and
    download specified data. Some attempt is made to simplify the API
    interface for the user.
URL: https://github.com/grahamrp/heidi
BugReports: https://github.com/grahamrp/heidi/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.0.3)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Imports:
    httr,
    RCurl,
    XML
Suggests: knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
